{"title":"采煤工人之歌","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":6,"day":6}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"采煤工人之歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工作面像战场，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风镐是矿工冲锋枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"煤层硬，怕什么？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让它向我们投降！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岩石想阻碍我们前进，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"安上炸药把它炸掉！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大水想要淹没矿井，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叫抽水机把它一下喝光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"井下的敌人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们一个也不怕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只要我们的风镐一响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地球就敞开了它的胸膛。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们抽开煤槽的闸板，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"煤炭像潮水一样倾泻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它要汇成一支巨流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流到祖国各个工业战线上。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":3,"page_end":3}